== Overview ==
The assault oriented Argon Laser uses a high density light beam to literally burn through its target. Like all Lasers, the weapon does relatively good levels of both shield and armor damage with a high degree of accuracy.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Argon Laser can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
